{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-002__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-002", "source_id": "song-lusong-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·002.1", "text_original": "有駜有駜，駜彼乘黃。夙夜在公，在公明明。\n振振鷺，鷺于下。鼓咽咽，醉言舞。于胥樂兮。", "text_normalized": "有駜有駜，駜彼乘黃。夙夜在公，在公明明。\n振振鷺，鷺于下。鼓咽咽，醉言舞。于胥樂兮。", "notes": "有駜 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-002__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-002", "source_id": "song-lusong-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·002.2", "text_original": "有駜有駜，駜彼乘牡。夙夜在公，在公飲酒。\n振振鷺，鷺于飛。鼓咽咽，醉言歸。于胥樂兮。", "text_normalized": "有駜有駜，駜彼乘牡。夙夜在公，在公飲酒。\n振振鷺，鷺于飛。鼓咽咽，醉言歸。于胥樂兮。", "notes": "有駜 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__song-lusong-002__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-lusong-002", "source_id": "song-lusong-002__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·魯頌·002.3", "text_original": "有駜有駜，駜彼乘駽。夙夜在公，在公載燕。\n自今以始，歲其有。君子有穀，詒孫子。于胥樂兮。", "text_normalized": "有駜有駜，駜彼乘駽。夙夜在公，在公載燕。\n自今以始，歲其有。君子有穀，詒孫子。于胥樂兮。", "notes": "有駜 Chinese stanza 3."}
